00:16:09,927 --> 00:16:11,011
Vanabelle.

249
00:16:14,431 --> 00:16:15,265
Kau tak apa?

250
00:16:16,183 --> 00:16:18,560
Lupakan aku, bunuh saja dia!

251
00:16:20,437 --> 00:16:21,605
Kita harus bergegas...

252
00:16:22,398 --> 00:16:23,732
mengakhiri penderitaannya.

253
00:16:33,492 --> 00:16:34,535
Vannie!

254
00:16:39,790 --> 00:16:40,666
Yah,

255
00:16:41,458 --> 00:16:42,876
kadang aku tak tahu lagi.

256
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:46,588
Kenapa aku di sini?

257
00:16:47,631 --> 00:16:50,426
Kenapa memburu naga?

258
00:16:51,552 --> 00:16:55,556
Aku terkejut mendengar kau punya keraguan
seperti itu.

259
00:16:56,640 --> 00:17:00,644
Aku belajar berlayar di langit
karena tak punya tempat di daratan.

260
00:17:02,688 --> 00:17:04,898
Karena aku tak punya tempat di daratan.

261
00:17:08,110 --> 00:17:08,944
Itu...

262
00:17:09,737 --> 00:17:10,696
Itu saja!

263
00:17:15,701 --> 00:17:17,828
Ukurannya menciut banyak.

264
00:17:18,203 --> 00:17:20,038
Kerja bagus. Kalian tak apa?

265
00:17:20,122 --> 00:17:21,081
Gibbs.

266
00:17:21,582 --> 00:17:23,917
Akan kubantu menyembelihnya.

267
00:17:24,168 --> 00:17:25,502
Kau nyaris tak bisa berdiri.

268
00:17:25,836 --> 00:17:29,465
Sejujurnya, kau terlalu sembrono.

269
00:17:32,426 --> 00:17:35,888
Tak ada gunanya membunuhnya
untuk menjaga rasanya jika kau mati.

270
00:17:35,971 --> 00:17:37,431
Aku takkan mati.

271
00:17:38,015 --> 00:17:41,685
Aku takkan mati sebelum memakannya.

272
00:17:42,811 --> 00:17:46,356
Buru, bunuh, dan makan.

273
00:17:47,816 --> 00:17:49,485
Itulah pekerjaan pemburu naga.

274
00:17:55,032 --> 00:17:58,410
Kembali ke Awan dan Kendarai Angin Baik
Sekali Lagi.

275
00:18:00,245 --> 00:18:01,246
Itu doa.

276
00:18:03,123 --> 00:18:04,166
Mika!

277
00:18:04,833 --> 00:18:06,251
Istirahatlah.

278
00:18:11,298 --> 00:18:12,841
Tikus besar.

279
00:18:13,967 --> 00:18:14,927
Vanabelle?

280
00:18:15,177 --> 00:18:16,512
Aku tak mencuri makanan.

281
00:18:17,012 --> 00:18:19,097
Bukankah kau tak bertugas?

282
00:18:19,473 --> 00:18:20,599
Aku tak bisa tidur.

283
00:18:21,809 --> 00:18:22,643
Apa itu?

284
00:18:22,893 --> 00:18:27,397
Aku mengambil hati naga
yang kita buru hari ini,

285
00:18:27,481 --> 00:18:30,275
dan memasaknya perlahan di minyak
dengan panci.

286
00:18:30,859 --> 00:18:33,445
Itu bukan mencuri makanan?

287
00:18:34,571 --> 00:18:35,739
Mau minum denganku?

288
00:18:36,657 --> 00:18:39,243
Ada sisa kentang dan acar kol.

289
00:18:40,035 --> 00:18:42,871
Bisa kau haluskan ini
dengan minyak dan garam?

290
00:18:42,955 --> 00:18:44,123
Apa yang kau lakukan?

291
00:18:44,414 --> 00:18:45,666
Memasak ala pedesaan.

292
00:18:46,500 --> 00:18:50,337
Minyaki loyang dan letakkan acar kol,

293
00:18:50,420 --> 00:18:54,007
lalu tekan dan isi
dengan kentang tumbuk serta confit hati.

294
00:18:55,592 --> 00:18:56,426
Mika.

295
00:18:57,678 --> 00:19:00,848
Kau selalu tersenyum saat memburu naga.

296
00:19:02,141 --> 00:19:03,350
Apa sungguh seasyik itu?

297
00:19:03,725 --> 00:19:04,852
Entahlah.

298
00:19:05,519 --> 00:19:06,353
Namun,

299
00:19:06,979 --> 00:19:08,230
aku yakin itu seru.

300
00:19:09,147 --> 00:19:09,982
Begitu.

301
00:19:12,651 --> 00:19:16,405
Setelah kau menekan semua bahan di loyang,

302
00:19:17,155 --> 00:19:22,119
keluarkan dengan hati-hati,
dan potong-potong.

303
00:19:22,202 --> 00:19:23,579
Luar biasa!

304
00:19:23,662 --> 00:19:25,622
TERRINE CONFIT HATI NAGA, KENTANG,
DAN ACAR KOL

305
00:19:29,793 --> 00:19:30,627
Enak sekali!

306
00:19:31,962 --> 00:19:33,922
Vanabelle, ini lezat!

307
00:19:34,214 --> 00:19:36,884
Renyah, mengenyangkan,
dan segar sekaligus!

308
00:19:37,217 --> 00:19:40,429
Kita hanya melapisinya,
tapi tetap menjadi hidangan lezat.

309
00:19:41,263 --> 00:19:42,556
Kau makan apa?

310
00:19:42,931 --> 00:19:44,349
Aku tak mencuri makanan!

311
00:19:44,725 --> 00:19:46,184
Vanabelle membuatnya!

312
00:19:46,351 --> 00:19:48,270
Bukan itu pertanyaanku.

313
00:19:48,395 --> 00:19:49,271
Kau baru selesai?

314
00:19:49,354 --> 00:19:52,858
- Ya, aku harus hangatkan diri.
- Kami akan mulai sif kami.

315
00:19:52,941 --> 00:19:54,860
Kalian hanya berdua saja?

316
00:19:55,235 --> 00:19:56,778
- Tak biasanya.
- Ya.

317
00:19:56,945 --> 00:19:58,113
Kelihatannya enak.

318
00:19:58,822 --> 00:20:00,365
- Biar kucoba.
- Hei!

319
00:20:02,451 --> 00:20:03,285
Enak!

320
00:20:03,368 --> 00:20:05,120
Sungguh? Aku juga mau coba.

321
00:20:06,330 --> 00:20:07,581
Itu punyaku.

322
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:08,999
Enak!

323
00:20:09,082 --> 00:20:11,376
Vannie, bisa buatkan lagi?

324
00:20:11,585 --> 00:20:14,212
Tentu, jika kau tak keberatan.

325
00:20:14,963 --> 00:20:15,797
Ini.

326
00:20:17,674 --> 00:20:18,717
Terima kasih.

327
00:20:18,800 --> 00:20:20,135
Hei, Mika.

328
00:20:21,011 --> 00:20:23,263
Kenapa kau bergabung di kapal ini?

329
00:20:24,056 --> 00:20:25,682
Bukankah sudah jelas?

330
00:20:26,016 --> 00:20:27,726
Aku suka naga.

331
00:20:29,895 --> 00:20:33,649
Memburunya, membunuhnya, memakannya.

332
00:20:34,191 --> 00:20:35,901
Aku juga suka hidup di kapal.

333
00:20:38,612 --> 00:20:40,948
Yang terpenting, ada di kapal ini

334
00:20:41,281 --> 00:20:43,367
berarti aku bisa selalu makan naga.

335
00:20:44,326 --> 00:20:47,120
Ada makanan lain yang enak.

336
00:20:49,456 --> 00:20:51,250
Namun naga yang paling enak.

337
00:21:07,516 --> 00:21:08,392
Teganya kau!

338
00:21:08,892 --> 00:21:10,519
Giraud memberitahuku.

339
00:21:10,727 --> 00:21:13,355
Kalian berpesta tanpa aku!

340
00:21:14,523 --> 00:21:15,357
Itu tak adil!

341
00:21:15,899 --> 00:21:18,151
Jangan keras-keras.

342
00:21:18,235 --> 00:21:19,194
Tak adil!

343
00:21:19,569 --> 00:21:21,530
Kenapa kalian tak bangunkan aku?

344
00:21:22,572 --> 00:21:23,907
Kau juga, Giraud!

345
00:21:23,991 --> 00:21:25,993
Kalian melupakanku!

346
00:21:27,452 --> 00:21:29,329
Berhenti tertawa, Vannie!

347
00:21:29,413 --> 00:21:31,581
Kenapa tak minta maaf?

348
